    "# ğŸ¬ Video Trimmer - Google Colab Edition\n",
    "\n",
    "A simplified video trimming tool with native Google Drive integration and awesome integrated controls.\n",
    "\n",
    "## âœ¨ Features:\n",
    "- ğŸ“ **Fast File Selection** - Direct path input (no slow searching)\n",
    "- ğŸ¥ **Integrated Video Player** - Video playback with trim controls together\n",
    "- ğŸµ **Audio Extraction** - Automatic AAC audio extraction\n",
    "- ğŸš€ **Fast Processing** - Uses ffmpeg for efficient video processing\n",
    "- ğŸ“± **Awesome UI** - Clean, integrated interface\n",
    "\n",
    "## ğŸš€ Quick Start:\n",
    "1. **Mount Google Drive** - Run the setup cell\n",
    "2. **Enter File Path** - Type or paste your video file path\n",
    "3. **Play & Trim** - Use the integrated player and trim controls\n",
    "4. **Process** - Click trim to generate output files\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
